# Public Vite env — baked into the client bundle at build time.
# Safe to commit: these are Supabase's public "anon" keys that are designed
# to ship in browsers. Row Level Security is what actually protects data.
#
# Real secrets (service_role keys, edge-function creds) belong in Supabase
# edge-function secrets, never here. See .env.example.

